{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"read"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"buffer","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sv","text":"UnsafeMutableRawPointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"count","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"CancellableRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gssize","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@gssize"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If count is zero returns zero and does nothing. A value of ","type":"text"},{"code":"count","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"larger than ","type":"text"},{"code":"G_MAXSSIZE","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will cause a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"type":"text","text":" error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On success, the number of bytes read into the buffer is returned.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. near the end of a file. Zero is returned on end of file"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(or if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"count"},{"type":"text","text":" is zero),  but never otherwise."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The returned ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"buffer"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a nul-terminated string, it can contain nul bytes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"at any position, and this function doesn’t nul-terminate the ","type":"text"},{"code":"buffer","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is not ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"was cancelled, the error ","type":"text"},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"partial result will be returned, without an error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On error -1 is returned and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" is set accordingly."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/pollableinputstreamref\/read(buffer:count:cancellable:)"]}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:3GIO19InputStreamProtocolPAAE4read6buffer5count11cancellableSiSvSg_SiAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO22PollableInputStreamRefV","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","title":"read(buffer:count:cancellable:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"read"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"b